<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.11">
<l>kaliyuka moṉṟumiṉ ṟikkē taṉṉaṭi yārkkaruḷ ceyyum</l>
<l>maliyuñ cuṭaroḷi mūrtti māyappi rāṉkaṇṇaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>kalivaya ṟeṉṉaṉ kurukūrk kārimā ṟaṉcaṭa kōpaṉ</l>
<l>olipuka ḻāyirat tippat tuḷḷattai mācaṟuk kummē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These ten in the thousand of sounding praise</l>
<l>by Kāri Māṟaṉ Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr of the Southern [king] with lush fields</l>
<l>on Kaṇṇaṉ, the miraculous lord with a glowing light form that is plentiful,</l>
<l>who does grace to his servants except once in the Kaliyuga,</l>
	<l>will cut off flaws from the mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
